ator-existing-pipeline\\\",\\\"category\\\":\\\"design-reference\\\",\\\"summary\\\":\\\"Shipped md-generator already provides a five-viewport measured extract-write-validate pipeline and v3 Style Reference schema with hard provenance failures.\\\",\\\"strategy\\\":\\\"FIELD_LEVEL_SCHEMA_COMPARISON_REQUIRED\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design-reference.md\\\"],\\\"sources\\\":[\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md:230-259\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/schema-v3.ts:90-120\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/schema-v3.ts:250-260\\\"]}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"styles-corpus-distinct-model\\\",\\\"category\\\":\\\"styles\\\",\\\"summary\\\":\\\"The sk-design styles surface is an authoritative flat extracted corpus with optional SQLite/FTS/vector retrieval and rights eligibility before ranking, not a curated named-theme catalog.\\\",\\\"strategy\\\":\\\"COEXISTENCE_QUESTION_REMAINS_OPEN\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/\\\"],\\\"sources\\\":[\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_db/README.md:1-5\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_db/README.md:52-65\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_db/README.md:87-100\\\"]}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":1,\\\"id\\\":\\\"roadmap-candidates-overlap-existing-surfaces\\\",\\\"category\\\":\\\"roadmap\\\",\\\"summary\\\":\\\"Hallmark roadmap candidates include brand-first flow, variants, motion tokens, data visualization, codebase study, image hooks, tactile guidance, multi-page coherence, and live-preview feedback; several names overlap shipped sk-design capabilities and need behavior-level comparison.\\\",\\\"strategy\\\":\\\"DO_NOT_CLASSIFY_BY_NAME_ALONE\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/de