{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784526779980,"sessionID":"ses_08202bafbffe7aMYl1BZMs5SAo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_7gugauXJgHhElDN2MUOzpixx","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-003.md\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 3\n+\n+Read config, state, strategy, registry, and prior iteration narratives first. Execute exactly one LEAF iteration; no sub-agents.\n+\n+## Focus\n+Compare Hallmark default `build` and explicit `redesign` behavior, especially `macrostructures.md`, `structure.md`, `component-cookbook.md`, `layout-and-space.md`, `references/verbs/redesign.md`, `responsive.md`, and relevant `preview-examples.md`, against shipped `sk-design` INTERFACE and FOUNDATIONS modes plus `/interface:design` and `/interface:foundations` command contracts. Determine whether sk-design already has a redesign equivalent and whether any separate redesign or variant command is justified. Extract concrete reusable structural heuristics and catalogs, but prefer surgical additions to existing references/procedures over new modes. Produce candidate matrix rows with exact target files, verdict, HOW, value, effort, and MIT copy-vs-learn treatment.\n+\n+## State\n+- Iteration 3 of 10; stopPolicy=max-iterations.\n+- Iteration 1 established license/inventory. Iteration 2 reconciled Hallmark's current slop suite as 58 gates and produced audit candidates.\n+- Do not revisit the completed gate-count comparison except where a structural rule directly informs interface/foundations.\n+\n+## Allowed Writes\n+- `.../sol-opencode/iterations/iteration-003.md`\n+- Append exactly one canonical iteration-3 record to `.../sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl`\n+- `.../sol-opencode/deltas/iter-003.jsonl`\n+Expand every `.../sol-opencode` prefix to `.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode`.\n+\n+No other writes. Use an append-safe operation for JSONL; do not use a context-dependent patch. Cite exact file:line evidence. Include Ruled Out and Dead Ends. The canonical state/delta record requires `type:\"iteration\"`, `iteration:3`, `run:3`, `mode:\"research\"`, `target_agent:\"deep-research\"`, `agent_definition_loaded:true`, `resolved_route:\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\"`, status, focus, findingsCount, newInfoRatio, noveltyJustification, keyQuestions, answeredQuestions, ruledOut, toolsUsed, sourcesQueried, timestamp, durationMs. Delta first line matches state, followed by structured findings/ruled_out rows. Verify all outputs and boundary.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-003.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-003.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-003.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-003.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,22 @@\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteratio