:"...output truncated...\n\nFull output saved to: /Users/michelkerkmeester/.local/share/opencode/tool-output/tool_f7e21a14e001Vs8r67QlXWj4va\n\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1784527822232,\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_Ffp7J4y9g1s1tOrrRiqv9mwU\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deltas/iter-004.jsonl\"},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deltas/iter-004.jsonl</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n1: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark color, typography, copy, imagery, custom direction, hero craft, floating navigation, and responsive quality versus shipped Interface and Foundations assets\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":9,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.83,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Six rows establish fully new file-level gaps and three refine prior inventory or responsive overlap into exact existing-file changes; (6 + 3*0.5) / 9 = 0.83.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which of the nine named Hallmark assets adds a real capability beyond shipped Interface and Foundations guidance?\\\",\\\"What exact existing file should own each useful rule without adding commands or presets?\\\",\\\"Which reuse choices require Hallmark notice or separate third-party rights handling?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"All nine named Hallmark assets now have exact target files, a COPY/ADAPT/LEARN/INSPIRE-NEW/SKIP verdict, a surgical change, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\\\",\\\"The highest-value gaps are signature-role hero selection, validated custom-craft evidence, fallback font metrics, authored-direction depth, and target-derived responsive proof.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\",\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\",\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\",\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\",\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"memory_match_triggers (timeout)\\\",\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"bash\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/color.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/typography.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/copy.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n2: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-1\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"color.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/color/palette-theming.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/assets/token-starter.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Require canonical palette and semantic role tokens to be opaque; model alpha only in explicitly named overlay, scrim, shadow, and optical-separator roles.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently restate the role rule; no notice. Copying Hallmark prose or palette recipes requires MIT notice.\\\"}\\n3: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-2\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"typography.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/type/typography-system.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/assets/token-starter.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add pairing and loading proof fields for display/body/utility role, source and rights, loaded weights, fallback family, size-adjust, ascent-override, descent-override, line-gap-override, and fallback-versus-loaded layout shift.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Native schema extension; do not copy the font catalog or fixed tone pairings.\\\"}\\n4: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-3\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"copy.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"LEARN / SKIP\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add latency-aware loading copy: silent for genuinely transient waits, operation label for perceptible waits, and real progress or an honest expectation for long waits; derive thresholds from measured product latency.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium-high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Idea-level rewrite needs no notice; do not copy attributed voice samples because Hallmark cannot establish quotation redistribution rights.\\\"}\\n5: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-4\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"imagery-kit.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"shared/creation-contract.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"INSPIRE-NEW\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add an optional owned-asset manifest inside the existing grounding/handoff envelope with stable owned URI, rights, attribution, dimensions, format, palette fit, intended role, checksum, fallback, and theme/mobile treatment.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium-high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"New native schema only. Never copy, hotlink, or redistribute Hallmark-hosted binaries; repository MIT does not establish those asset rights.\\\"}\\n6: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-5\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"custom-theme.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/procedures/aesthetic-direction.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Classify direction as precedent-grounded, authored-tuned, or authored-bespoke. Use tuned only for explicit brand tokens or unsupported multi-attribute direction, bespoke only when composition itself is the ask; preserve owned systems, label authored values, preview palette/type/structure, and retain the same proof floor.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"very high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently worded routing; no catalog, axis names, stamps, or worked palettes copied.\\\"}\\n7: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-6\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"custom-craft.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Replace the blanket hand-built-SVG prohibition with a ban on unvalidated fallback art. Permit brief-grounded CSS/SVG only with purpose, reuse search, provenance, semantic labeling, bundle cost, fallback, reduced-motion behavior, and render proof.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Adapt the evidence contract only; do not copy recipes, vendor claims, support percentages, or fixed budgets.\\\"}\\n8: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-7\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"hero-enrichment.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/procedures/aesthetic-direction.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Replace mandatory hero/page imagery with a signature-role decision: typography, owned media, real product proof, generated asset, or explicit placeholder. When media exists require source, subject, crop/aspect, mobile transformation, load priority, alt/captions, and reduced-motion behavior; typography-only passes when brief-grounded.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"very high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low-medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Native correction with independent wording; do not import the eight-archetype catalog.\\\"}\\n9: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-8\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"floating-nav.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/procedures/prototype-flow-spec.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"LEARN\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add a stateful morph proof row: one semantic DOM owner, invariant layout geometry, explicit per-state property ownership, transform-only visual offset, one timing family, keyboard/focus behavior, reduced motion, and scroll performance evidence.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low-medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Learn the invariant/property-ownership method; do not copy exact CSS, 520 ms timing, threshold, or shadow recipe.\\\"}\\n10: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-9\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"responsive.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/layout/layout-responsive.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/references/layout/adaptation-matrix.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add a target-derived verification matrix covering minimum supported width, every content transition, one intermediate width, zoom/text expansion, portrait/landscape, pointer/hover, safe areas, horizontal overflow, unbreakable content, image-track zero minimums, wrapped affordances, and focus-induced scroll jumps.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently worded proof matrix; Hallmark widths may appear only as a labeled marketing-web example, never doctrine.\\\"}\\n11: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-1\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\"}\\n12: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-2\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\"}\\n13: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-3\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\"}\\n14: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-4\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\"}\\n15: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-5\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"}\\n\\n(End of file - total 15 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark color, typography, copy, imagery, custom direct