rty ownership, transform-only visual offset, one timing family, keyboard/focus behavior, reduced motion, and scroll performance evidence.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low-medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Learn the invariant/property-ownership method; do not copy exact CSS, 520 ms timing, threshold, or shadow recipe.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-9\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"responsive.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/layout/layout-responsive.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/references/layout/adaptation-matrix.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add a target-derived verification matrix covering minimum supported width, every content transition, one intermediate width, zoom/text expansion, portrait/landscape, pointer/hover, safe areas, horizontal overflow, unbreakable content, image-track zero minimums, wrapped affordances, and focus-induced scroll jumps.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently worded proof matrix; Hallmark widths may appear only as a labeled marketing-web example, never doctrine.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-1\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-2\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-3\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-4\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-5\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"}\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[],\"display\":{\"type\":\"file\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deltas/iter-004.jsonl\",\"text\":\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark color, typography, copy, imagery, custom direction, hero craft, floating navigation, and responsive quality versus shipped Interface and Foundations assets\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":9,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.83,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Six rows establish fully new file-level gaps and three refine prior inventory or responsive overlap into exact existing-file changes; (6 + 3*0.5) / 9 = 0.83.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which of the nine named Hallmark assets adds a real capability beyond shipped Interface and Foundations guidance?\\\",\\\"What exact existing file should own each useful rule without adding commands or presets?\\\",\\\"Which reuse choices require Hallmark notice or separate third-party rights handling?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"All nine named Hallmark assets now have exact target files, a COPY/ADAPT/LEARN/INSPIRE-NEW/SKIP verdict, a surgical change, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\\\",\\\"The highest-value gaps are signature-role hero selection, validated custom-craft evidence, fallback font metrics, authored-direction depth, and target-derived responsive proof.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\",\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\",\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\",\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\",\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"memory_match_triggers (timeout)\\\",\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"bash\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/color.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/typography.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/copy.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-1\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"color.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/color/palette-theming.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/assets/token-starter.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Require canonical palette and semantic role tokens to be opaque; model alpha only in explicitly named overlay, scrim, shadow, and optical-separator roles.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently restate the role rule; no notice. Copying Hallmark prose or palette recipes requires MIT notice.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-2\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"typography.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/type/typography-system.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/assets/token-starter.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add pairing and loading proof fields for display/body/utility role, source and rights, loaded weights, fallback family, size-adjust, ascent-override, descent-override, line-gap-override, and fallback-versus-loaded layout shift.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Native schema extension; do not copy the font catalog or fixed tone pairings.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-3\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"copy.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"LEARN / SKIP\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add latency-aware loading copy: silent for genuinely transient waits, operation label for perceptible waits, and real progress or an honest expectation for long waits; derive thresholds from measured product latency.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium-high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Idea-level rewrite needs no notice; do not copy attributed voice samples because Hallmark cannot establish quotation redistribution rights.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-4\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"imagery-kit.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"shared/creation-contract.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"INSPIRE-NEW\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add an optional owned-asset manifest inside the existing grounding/handoff envelope with stable owned URI, rights, attribution, dimensions, format, palette fit, intended role, checksum, fallback, and theme/mobile treatment.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium-high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"New native schema only. Never copy, hotlink, or redistribute Hallmark-hosted binaries; repository MIT does not establish those asset rights.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-5\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"custom-theme.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/procedures/aesthetic-direction.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Classify direction as precedent-grounded, authored-tuned, or authored-bespoke. Use tuned only for explicit brand tokens or unsupported multi-attribute direction, bespoke only when composition itself is the ask; preserve owned systems, label authored values, preview palette/type/structure, and retain the same proof floor.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"very high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently worded routing; no catalog, axis names, stamps, or worked palettes copied.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-6\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"custom-craft.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Replace the blanket hand-built-SVG prohibition with a ban on unvalidated fallback art. Permit brief-grounded CSS/SVG only with purpose, reuse search, provenance, semantic labeling, bundle cost, fallback, reduced-motion behavior, and render proof.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Adapt the evidence contract only; do not copy recipes, vendor claims, support percentages, or fixed budgets.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-7\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"hero-enrichment.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/procedures/aesthetic-direction.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Replace mandatory hero/page imagery with a signature-role decision: typography, owned media, real product proof, generated asset, or explicit placeholder. When media exists require source, subject, crop/aspect, mobile transformation, load priority, alt/captions, and reduced-motion behavior; typography-only passes when brief-grounded.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"very high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low-medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Native correction with independent wording; do not import the eight-archetype catalog.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-8\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"floating-nav.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/procedures/prototype-flow-spec.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"LEARN\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add a stateful morph proof row: one semantic DOM owner, invariant layout geometry, explicit per-state property ownership, transform-only visual offset, one timing family, keyboard/focus behavior, reduced motion, and scroll performance evidence.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low-medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Learn the invariant/property-ownership method; do not copy exact CSS, 520 ms timing, threshold, or shadow recipe.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-9\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"responsive.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/layout/layout-responsive.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/references/layout/adaptation-matrix.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add a target-derived verification matrix covering minimum supported width, every content transition, one intermediate width, zoom/text expansion, portrait/landscape, pointer/hover, safe areas, horizontal overflow, unbreakable content, image-track zero minimums, wrapped affordances, and focus-induced scroll jumps.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently worded proof matrix; Hallmark widths may appear only as a labeled marketing-web example, never doctrine.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-1\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-2\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-3\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-4\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-5\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"}\",\"lineStart\":1,\"lineEnd\":15,\"totalLines\":15,\"truncated\":false}},\"title\":\".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deltas/iter-004.jsonl\",\"time\":{\"start\":1784527822215,\"end\":1784527822230}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_0410cd5e233cee39016a5dbbce140081919652621c2be06e50\"}},\"id\":\"prt_f7e259d84001EONW7NSwBQxg54\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e2569c20018Iw9iXn4RnVBwk\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1784527822244,\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_Chloo02PcYAD1Dc69JNxJ4jt\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl\",\"offset\":4,\"limit\":2},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n4: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":3,\\\"run\\\":3,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark default build and redesign behavior versus shipped interface and foundations contracts\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":11,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.86,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Eight rows establish new redesign, route, scope, and structural-catalog decisions; three refine prior overlap into exact surgical targets.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Does shipped sk-design already have a redesign equivalent?\\\",\\\"Is a separate redesign or variant command justified?\\\",\\\"Which Hallmark structural heuristics and catalogs merit surgical reuse?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Shipped design-interface and /interface:design already provide redesign and multi-direction equivalents.\\\",\\\"No separate redesign or variant command is justified.\\\",\\\"Multi-surface coherence and generation-time structural option framing are the highest-value surgical additions.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"A separate redesign mode or command\\\",\\\"A separate variant command\\\",\\\"Copying the 21 macrostructures or 50 component archetypes as presets\\\",\\\"Replacing foundations responsive guidance with fixed viewport recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/macrostructures.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/structure.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/component-cookbook.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/layout-and-space.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/verbs/redesign.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/responsive.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/preview-examples.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/**\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/i... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n5: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark color, typography, copy, imagery, custom direction, hero craft, floating navigation, and responsive quality versus shipped Interface and Foundations assets\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":9,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.83,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Six rows establish fully new file-level gaps and three refine prior inventory or responsive overlap into exact existing-file changes; (6 + 3*0.5) / 9 = 0.83.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which of the nine named Hallmark assets adds a real capability beyond shipped Interface and Foundations guidance?\\\",\\\"What exact existing file should own each useful rule without adding commands or presets?\\\",\\\"Which reuse choices require Hallmark notice or separate third-party rights handling?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"All nine named Hallmark assets now have exact target files, a COPY/ADAPT/LEARN/INSPIRE-NEW/SKIP verdict, a surgical change, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\\\",\\\"The highest-value gaps are signature-role hero selection, validated custom-craft evidence, fallback font metrics, authored-direction depth, and target-derived responsive proof.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\",\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\",\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\",\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\",\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"memory_match_triggers (timeout)\\\",\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"bash\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/color.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/typography.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/copy.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n\\n(End of file - total 5 lines)\\n</content>\",\"metadata\":{\"preview\":\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":3,\\\"run\\\":3,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark default build and redesign behavior versus shipped interface and foundations contracts\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":11,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.86,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Eight rows establish new redesign, route, scope, and structural-catalog decisions; three refine prior overlap into exact surgical targets.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Does shipped sk-design already have a redesign equivalent?\\\",\\\"Is a separate redesign or variant command justified?\\\",\\\"Which Hallmark structural heuristics and catalogs merit surgical reuse?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Shipped design-interface and /interface:design already provide redesign and multi-direction equivalents.\\\",\\\"No separate redesign or variant command is justified.\\\",\\\"Multi-surface coherence and generation-time structural option framing are the highest-value surgical additions.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"A separate redesign mode or command\\\",\\\"A separate variant command\\\",\\\"Copying the 21 macrostructures or 50 component archetypes as presets\\\",\\\"Replacing foundations responsive guidance with fixed viewport recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/macrostructures.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/structure.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/component-cookbook.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/layout-and-space.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/verbs/redesign.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/responsive.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/preview-examples.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/**\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/i... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark color, typography, copy, imagery, custom direction, hero craft, floating navigation, and responsive quality versus shipped Interface and Foundations assets\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":9,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.83,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Six rows establish fully new file-level gaps and three refine prior inventory or responsive overlap into exact existing-file changes; (6 + 3*0.5) / 9 = 0.83.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which of the nine named Hallmark assets adds a real capability beyond shipped Interface and Foundations guidance?\\\",\\\"What exact existing file should own each useful rule without adding commands or presets?\\\",\\\"Which reuse choices require Hallmark notice or separate third-party rights handling?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"All nine named Hallmark assets now have exact target files, a COPY/ADAPT/LEARN/INSPIRE-NEW/SKIP verdict, a surgical change, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\\\",\\\"The highest-value gaps are signature-role hero selection, validated custom-craft evidence, fallback font metrics, authored-direction depth, and target-derived responsive proof.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\",\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\",\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\",\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\",\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"memory_match_triggers (timeout)\\\",\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"bash\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/color.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/typography.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/copy.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[],\"display\":{\"type\":\"file\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl\",\"text\":\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":3,\\\"run\\\":3,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark default build and redesign behavior versus shipped interface and foundations contracts\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":11,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.86,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Eight rows establish new redesign, route, scope, and structural-catalog decisions; three refine prior overlap into exact surgical targets.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Does shipped sk-design already have a redesign equivalent?\\\",\\\"Is a separate redesign or variant command justified?\\\",\\\"Which Hallmark structural heuristics and catalogs merit surgical reuse?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Shipped design-interface and /interface:design already provide redesign and multi-direction equivalents.\\\",\\\"No separate redesign or variant command is justified.\\\",\\\"Multi-surface coherence and generation-time structural option framing are the highest-value surgical additions.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"A separate redesign mode or command\\\",\\\"A separate variant command\\\",\\\"Copying the 21 macrostructures or 50 component archetypes as presets\\\",\\\"Replacing foundations responsive guidance with fixed viewport recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/macrostructures.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/structure.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/component-cookbook.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/layout-and-space.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/verbs/redesign.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/responsive.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/preview-examples.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/**\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/i... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark color, typography, copy, imagery, custom direction, hero craft, floating navigation, and responsive quality versus shipped Interface and Foundations assets\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":9,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.83,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Six rows establish fully new file-level gaps and three refine prior inventory or responsive overlap into exact existing-file changes; (6 + 3*0.5) / 9 = 0.83.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which of the nine named Hallmark assets adds a real capability beyond shipped Interface and Foundations guidance?\\\",\\\"What exact existing file should own each useful rule without adding commands or presets?\\\",\\\"Which reuse choices require Hallmark notice or separate third-party rights handling?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"All nine named Hallmark assets now have exact target files, a COPY/ADAPT/LEARN/INSPIRE-NEW/SKIP verdict, a surgical change, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\\\",\\\"The highest-value gaps are signature-role hero selection, validated custom-craft evidence, fallback font metrics, authored-direction depth, and target-derived responsive proof.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\",\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\",\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\",\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\",\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"memory_match_triggers (timeout)\\\",\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"bash\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/color.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/typography.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/copy.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\",\"lineStart\":4,\"lineEnd\":5,\"totalLines\":5,\"truncated\":false}},\"title\":\".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl\",\"time\":{\"start\":1784527822241,\"end\":1784527822243}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_0410cd5e233cee39016a5dbbce14a081918ac78b82b9945f14\"}},\"id\":\"prt_f7e259d88001im1cPHOGw0VkPv\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e2569c20018Iw9iXn4RnVBwk\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1784527822304,\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"call_YjYwmCXi6QO2TalcxrtxCaA0\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"git status --short -- \\\".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode\\\" && git diff --check -- \\\".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode\\\"\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public\",\"timeout\":120000},\"output\":\"?? .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/\\n\",\"metadata\":{\"output\":\"?? .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/\\n\",\"exit\":0,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"git status --short -- \\\".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode\\\" && git diff --check -- \\\".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode\\\"\",\"time\":{\"start\":1784527822284,\"end\":1784527822298}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_0410cd5e233cee39016a5dbbce15e48191bca423beee599478\"}},\"id\":\"prt_f7e259da7001mEaxt0KdtKIKzr\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e2569c20018Iw9iXn4RnVBwk\"}}\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1784527823561,\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f7e25a2c7001YVwAFVa7iNVDno\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"fe03b20dde9c4dbba7dc0e6f79ecce2c3c838fcc\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e2569c20018Iw9iXn4RnVBwk\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":186101,\"input\":9959,\"output\":346,\"reasoning\":180,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":175616}},\"cost\":0}}\n{\"type\":\"step_start\",\"timestamp\":1784527829107,\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f7e25b871001CSzS5KhCY0VcVF\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e25a79b001gQurrQiknhlTsz\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"snapshot\":\"fe03b20dde9c4dbba7dc0e6f79ecce2c3c838fcc\",\"type\":\"step-start\"}}\n{\"type\":\"text\",\"timestamp\":1784527834461,\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f7e25c473001xZA8P07OQxLrA1\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e25a79b001gQurrQiknhlTsz\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Iteration 4 executed as a single LEAF research iteration.\\n\\nCreated:\\n- `iterations/iteration-004.md`\\n- `deltas/iter-004.jsonl`\\n\\nAppended:\\n- One iteration-4 record to `deep-research-state.jsonl`\\n\\nVerification passed:\\n- Exactly one canonical iteration-4 state record\\n- Delta first row exactly matches canonical state\\n- 9 structured findings and 5 ruled-out rows\\n- `git diff --check` passed\\n- No writes outside the three permitted outputs\\n\\n`newInfoRatio: 0.83`; status remains `complete` for iteration 4, with the ten-iteration loop continuing.\",\"time\":{\"start\":1784527832179,\"end\":1784527834460},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"msg_0dd7008b22ce5a25016a5dbbd826948191bcb5600a2ad9e035\",\"phase\":\"final_answer\"}}}}\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1784527835630,\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f7e25d1ec001sYGXgdPMHMVhNa\",\"reason\":\"stop\",\"snapshot\":\"fe03b20dde9c4dbba7dc0e6f79ecce2c3c838fcc\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e25a79b001gQurrQiknhlTsz\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"type\":\"step-finish\",\"tokens\":{\"total\":194514,\"input\":9395,\"output\":138,\"reasoning\":149,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":184832}},\"cost\":0}}\nOK iteration 4 complete: narrative + route-proof + delta\n[deep-research] detected 5 legacy-import question(s) in key-questions; append external questions to research/inbox.jsonl instead.\n{\"iterationsCompleted\":4}\n","metadata":{"output":"...\n\n\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-9\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"responsive.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/layout/layout-responsive.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/references/layout/adaptation-matrix.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add a target-derived verification matrix covering minimum supported width, every content transition, one intermediate width, zoom/text expansion, portrait/landscape, pointer/hover, safe areas, horizontal overflow, unbreakable content, image-track zero minimums, wrapped affordances, and focus-induced scroll jumps.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently worded proof matrix; Hallmark widths may appear only as a labeled marketing-web example, never doctrine.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-1\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-2\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-3\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-4\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-5\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"}\",\"truncated\":false,\"loaded\":[],\"display\":{\"type\":\"file\",\"path\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deltas/iter-004.jsonl\",\"text\":\"{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark color, typography, copy, imagery, custom direction, hero craft, floating navigation, and responsive quality versus shipped Interface and Foundations assets\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":9,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.83,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Six rows establish fully new file-level gaps and three refine prior inventory or responsive overlap into exact existing-file changes; (6 + 3*0.5) / 9 = 0.83.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which of the nine named Hallmark assets adds a real capability beyond shipped Interface and Foundations guidance?\\\",\\\"What exact existing file should own each useful rule without adding commands or presets?\\\",\\\"Which reuse choices require Hallmark notice or separate third-party rights handling?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"All nine named Hallmark assets now have exact target files, a COPY/ADAPT/LEARN/INSPIRE-NEW/SKIP verdict, a surgical change, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\\\",\\\"The highest-value gaps are signature-role hero selection, validated custom-craft evidence, fallback font metrics, authored-direction depth, and target-derived responsive proof.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\",\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\",\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\",\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\",\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"memory_match_triggers (timeout)\\\",\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"bash\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/color.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/typography.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/copy.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-1\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"color.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/color/palette-theming.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/assets/token-starter.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Require canonical palette and semantic role tokens to be opaque; model alpha only in explicitly named overlay, scrim, shadow, and optical-separator roles.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently restate the role rule; no notice. Copying Hallmark prose or palette recipes requires MIT notice.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-2\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"typography.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/type/typography-system.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/assets/token-starter.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add pairing and loading proof fields for display/body/utility role, source and rights, loaded weights, fallback family, size-adjust, ascent-override, descent-override, line-gap-override, and fallback-versus-loaded layout shift.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Native schema extension; do not copy the font catalog or fixed tone pairings.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-3\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"copy.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"LEARN / SKIP\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add latency-aware loading copy: silent for genuinely transient waits, operation label for perceptible waits, and real progress or an honest expectation for long waits; derive thresholds from measured product latency.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium-high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Idea-level rewrite needs no notice; do not copy attributed voice samples because Hallmark cannot establish quotation redistribution rights.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-4\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"imagery-kit.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"shared/creation-contract.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"INSPIRE-NEW\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add an optional owned-asset manifest inside the existing grounding/handoff envelope with stable owned URI, rights, attribution, dimensions, format, palette fit, intended role, checksum, fallback, and theme/mobile treatment.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium-high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"New native schema only. Never copy, hotlink, or redistribute Hallmark-hosted binaries; repository MIT does not establish those asset rights.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-5\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"custom-theme.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/procedures/aesthetic-direction.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Classify direction as precedent-grounded, authored-tuned, or authored-bespoke. Use tuned only for explicit brand tokens or unsupported multi-attribute direction, bespoke only when composition itself is the ask; preserve owned systems, label authored values, preview palette/type/structure, and retain the same proof floor.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"very high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently worded routing; no catalog, axis names, stamps, or worked palettes copied.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-6\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"custom-craft.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Replace the blanket hand-built-SVG prohibition with a ban on unvalidated fallback art. Permit brief-grounded CSS/SVG only with purpose, reuse search, provenance, semantic labeling, bundle cost, fallback, reduced-motion behavior, and render proof.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Adapt the evidence contract only; do not copy recipes, vendor claims, support percentages, or fixed budgets.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-7\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"hero-enrichment.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/procedures/aesthetic-direction.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Replace mandatory hero/page imagery with a signature-role decision: typography, owned media, real product proof, generated asset, or explicit placeholder. When media exists require source, subject, crop/aspect, mobile transformation, load priority, alt/captions, and reduced-motion behavior; typography-only passes when brief-grounded.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"very high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low-medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Native correction with independent wording; do not import the eight-archetype catalog.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-8\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"floating-nav.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-interface/procedures/prototype-flow-spec.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"LEARN\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add a stateful morph proof row: one semantic DOM owner, invariant layout geometry, explicit per-state property ownership, transform-only visual offset, one timing family, keyboard/focus behavior, reduced motion, and scroll performance evidence.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"low-medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Learn the invariant/property-ownership method; do not copy exact CSS, 520 ms timing, threshold, or shadow recipe.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"finding\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-finding-9\\\",\\\"asset\\\":\\\"responsive.md\\\",\\\"targets\\\":[\\\"design-foundations/references/layout/layout-responsive.md\\\",\\\"design-foundations/references/layout/adaptation-matrix.md\\\",\\\"design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\"],\\\"verdict\\\":\\\"ADAPT\\\",\\\"change\\\":\\\"Add a target-derived verification matrix covering minimum supported width, every content transition, one intermediate width, zoom/text expansion, portrait/landscape, pointer/hover, safe areas, horizontal overflow, unbreakable content, image-track zero minimums, wrapped affordances, and focus-induced scroll jumps.\\\",\\\"value\\\":\\\"high\\\",\\\"effort\\\":\\\"medium\\\",\\\"licensing\\\":\\\"Independently worded proof matrix; Hallmark widths may appear only as a labeled marketing-web example, never doctrine.\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-1\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-2\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-3\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-4\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\"}\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"ruled_out\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"id\\\":\\\"iter-004-ruled-5\\\",\\\"reason\\\":\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"}\",\"lineStart\":1,\"lineEnd\":15,\"totalLines\":15,\"truncated\":false}},\"title\":\".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deltas/iter-004.jsonl\",\"time\":{\"start\":1784527822215,\"end\":1784527822230}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_0410cd5e233cee39016a5dbbce140081919652621c2be06e50\"}},\"id\":\"prt_f7e259d84001EONW7NSwBQxg54\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e2569c20018Iw9iXn4RnVBwk\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1784527822244,\"sessionID\":\"ses_081dff6efffeBIwsf0Sts1EyUS\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_Chloo02PcYAD1Dc69JNxJ4jt\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl\",\"offset\":4,\"limit\":2},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n4: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":3,\\\"run\\\":3,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark default build and redesign behavior versus shipped interface and foundations contracts\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":11,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.86,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Eight rows establish new redesign, route, scope, and structural-catalog decisions; three refine prior overlap into exact surgical targets.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Does shipped sk-design already have a redesign equivalent?\\\",\\\"Is a separate redesign or variant command justified?\\\",\\\"Which Hallmark structural heuristics and catalogs merit surgical reuse?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Shipped design-interface and /interface:design already provide redesign and multi-direction equivalents.\\\",\\\"No separate redesign or variant command is justified.\\\",\\\"Multi-surface coherence and generation-time structural option framing are the highest-value surgical additions.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"A separate redesign mode or command\\\",\\\"A separate variant command\\\",\\\"Copying the 21 macrostructures or 50 component archetypes as presets\\\",\\\"Replacing foundations responsive guidance with fixed viewport recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/macrostructures.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/structure.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/component-cookbook.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/layout-and-space.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/verbs/redesign.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/responsive.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/preview-examples.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/**\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/i... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n5: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"a