 complete Hallmark/sk-design asset inventory\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":8,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":1.0,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"First evidence pass established the MIT authority and notice obligation, grouped Hallmark inventory, and concrete shipped sk-design target map where no prior findings existed.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"What does Hallmark's license permit and require?\\\",\\\"Which Hallmark assets map to each sk-design surface?\\\",\\\"Which slop gates, critique heuristics, schema fields, motion tokens, and DNA fields are absent or weaker?\\\",\\\"How should Hallmark themes and the sk-design styles corpus coexist?\\\",\\\"Which roadmap ideas merit adaptation, new capabilities, or rejection?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Hallmark is MIT-licensed: use, copy, modify, merge, publish, distribute, sublicense, and sale are permitted, but the copyright and permission notice must accompany copies or substantial portions.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"README licensing shorthand as the complete legal condition\\\",\\\"Assuming portable design.md is absent from shipped sk-design\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/LICENSE\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/README.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/ROADMAP.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/SKILL.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/mode-registry.json\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/command-metadata.json\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-{interface,foundations,motion,audit,md-generator}/SKILL.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/procedures/ai-slop-check.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/schema-v3.ts\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design-reference.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_db/README.md\\\"],\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-07-20T05:33:57Z\\\",\\\"durationMs\\\":285000}\\n {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":2,\\\"run\\\":2,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Gate-by-gate Hallmark slop and audit comparison against shipped sk-design design-audit\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":17,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.82,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Resolved the 57/58 discrepancy, established the shipped evidence and severity contract as authoritative, and produced seventeen path-specific adoption or rejection candidates absent from iteration 1's inventory.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Why do Hallmark sources disagree between 57 and 58 gates?\\\",\\\"Which Hallmark gates or heuristics are absent, weaker, redundant, or inappropriate in shipped design-audit?\\\",\\\"Which concrete target paths merit COPY, ADAPT, LEARN, INSPIRE-NEW, or SKIP, and when is MIT notice required?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"The current checklist has integer gates 1-57 plus distinct gate 38a, totaling 58; README's 57 is stale.\\\",\\\"Shipped audit has stronger evidence, severity, readiness, scoring, and owner-routing semantics, while Hallmark is more granular on structural fingerprints, fabricated content, fake chrome, input geometry, and responsive edge cases.\\\",\\\"No direct COPY is recommended; independently worded adaptations avoid notice, while copied axis tables, detailed gate prose, recipes, or substantial anti-pattern entries require the Hallmark MIT notice.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Treating README's 57 as evidence that a current gate is missing\\\",\\\"Replacing shipped P0-P3 severity with Hallmark critical/major/minor labels\\\",\\\"Copying all 58 gates wholesale into design-audit\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/slop-test.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/anti-patterns.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/verbs/audit.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/README.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/LICENSE\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/SKILL.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/references/audit-contract.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/procedures/ai-slop-check.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/references/anti-patterns-production.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/references/ai-fingerprint-tells.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/assets/ai-fingerprint-registry.json\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/assets/anti-patterns-score-rubric.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/assets/ai-fingerprint-self-defect-card.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/manual-testing-playbook/slop-hardening/anti-slop-production-hardening.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/manual-testing-playbook/slop-hardening/ai-fingerprint-tells.md\\\"],\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-07-20T05:48:41Z\\\",\\\"durationMs\\\":510000}\\n {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":3,\\\"run\\\":3,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark default build and redesign behavior versus shipped interface and foundations contracts\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":11,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.86,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Eight rows establish new redesign, route, scope, and structural-catalog decisions; three refine prior overlap into exact surgical targets.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Does shipped sk-design already have a redesign equivalent?\\\",\\\"Is a separate redesign or variant command justified?\\\",\\\"Which Hallmark structural heuristics and catalogs merit surgical reuse?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Shipped design-interface and /interface:design already provide redesign and multi-direction equivalents.\\\",\\\"No separate redesign or variant command is justified.\\\",\\\"Multi-surface coherence and generation-time structural option framing are the highest-value surgical additions.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"A separate redesign mode or command\\\",\\\"A separate variant command\\\",\\\"Copying the 21 macrostructures or 50 component archetypes as presets\\\",\\\"Replacing foundations responsive guidance with fixed viewport recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/macrostructures.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/structure.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/component-cookbook.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/layout-and-space.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/verbs/redesign.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/responsive.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/preview-examples.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/**\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/foundations.md\\\"],\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-07-20T05:55:38Z\\\",\\\"durationMs\\\":620000}\\n {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":4,\\\"run\\\":4,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark color, typography, copy, imagery, custom direction, hero craft, floating navigation, and responsive quality versus shipped Interface and Foundations assets\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":9,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.83,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Six rows establish fully new file-level gaps and three refine prior inventory or responsive overlap into exact existing-file changes; (6 + 3*0.5) / 9 = 0.83.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which of the nine named Hallmark assets adds a real capability beyond shipped Interface and Foundations guidance?\\\",\\\"What exact existing file should own each useful rule without adding commands or presets?\\\",\\\"Which reuse choices require Hallmark notice or separate third-party rights handling?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"All nine named Hallmark assets now have exact target files, a COPY/ADAPT/LEARN/INSPIRE-NEW/SKIP verdict, a surgical change, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\\\",\\\"The highest-value gaps are signature-role hero selection, validated custom-craft evidence, fallback font metrics, authored-direction depth, and target-derived responsive proof.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\",\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\",\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\",\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\",\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"memory_match_triggers (timeout)\\\",\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"bash\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/color.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/typography.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/copy.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/imagery-kit.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/custom-theme.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/custom-craft.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/hero-enrichment.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/floating-nav.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/responsive.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/color/palette-theming.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/assets/token-starter.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/type/typography-system.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/layout/layout-responsive.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/layout/adaptation-matrix.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/procedures/aesthetic-direction.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/procedures/prototype-flow-spec.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/creation-contract.md\\\"],\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-07-20T06:10:06.551Z\\\",\\\"durationMs\\\":780000}\\n+{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":5,\\\"run\\\":5,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"@deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\\\",\\\"execution\\\":\\\"single_iteration\\\",\\\"state_source\\\":\\\"externalized_files\\\",\\\"do_not_switch_mode\\\":true,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark motion, microinteractions, and interaction states versus shipped Motion, /interface:motion, Foundations tokens, and Interface state guidance\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":8,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.81,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Five findings establish new file-level gaps or ownership decisions and three refine known motion overlap into exact surgical targets; (5 + 3*0.5) / 8 = 0.81 after rounding.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Are Hallmark's theme-aware motion tokens worth adopting, and where should they live?\\\",\\\"Which motion, microinteraction, async-state, interruption, reduced-motion, and performance rules are absent or weaker in shipped sk-design?\\\",\\\"Does any gap justify a new command or preset catalog?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Adopt a native semantic motion-modifier schema in existing Motion and Foundations assets, but reject Hallmark's named theme multipliers as presets.\\\",\\\"Shipped Motion is stronger on route-level interruption/reversal, async state modeling, reduced-motion semantic parity, and performance verification; card propagation and three async feedback checks are the narrow gaps.\\\",\\\"No new command is justified; all useful changes fit existing Motion, Foundations, and Interface owners.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"A new theme-motion, microinteraction, interaction-state, or reduced-motion command\\\",\\\"Hallmark's ten-theme duration multiplier table as presets\\\",\\\"A universal eight-state mandate for every interactive element\\\",\\\"Hallmark's global 150ms-important reduced-motion recipe and absolute transform-opacity-only rule\\\",\\\"Copying exact duration, easing, spring, stagger, tooltip, toast, or drag recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/motion.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/microinteractions.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/interaction-and-states.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/motion.md\\\",\\\".openc