copied axis tables, detailed gate prose, recipes, or substantial anti-pattern entries require the Hallmark MIT notice.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Treating README's 57 as evidence that a current gate is missing\\\",\\\"Replacing shipped P0-P3 severity with Hallmark critical/major/minor labels\\\",\\\"Copying all 58 gates wholesale into design-audit\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/slop-test.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/anti-patterns.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/verbs/audit.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/README.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/LICENSE\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/SKILL.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/references/audit-contract.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/procedures/ai-slop-check.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/references/anti-patterns-production.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/references/ai-fingerprint-tells.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/assets/ai-fingerprint-registry.json\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/assets/anti-patterns-score-rubric.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/assets/ai-fingerprint-self-defect-card.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/manual-testing-playbook/slop-hardening/anti-slop-production-hardening.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-audit/manual-testing-playbook/slop-hardening/ai-fingerprint-tells.md\\\"],\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-07-20T05:48:41Z\\\",\\\"durationMs\\\":510000}\\n {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":3,\\\"run\\\":3,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark default build and redesign behavior versus shipped interface and foundations contracts\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":11,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.86,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Eight rows establish new redesign, route, scope, and structural-catalog decisions; three refine prior overlap into exact surgical targets.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Does shipped sk-design already have a redesign equivalent?\\\",\\\"Is a separate redesign or variant command justified?\\\",\\\"Which Hallmark structural heuristics and catalogs merit surgical reuse?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Shipped design-interface and /interface:design already provide redesign and multi-direction equivalents.\\\",\\\"No separate redesign or variant command is justified.\\\",\\\"Multi-surface coherence and generation-time structural option framing are the highest-value surgical additions.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"A separate redesign mode or command\\\",\\\"A separate variant command\\\",\\\"Copying the 21 macrostructures or 50 component archetypes as presets\\\",\\\"Replacing foundations responsive guidance with fixed viewport recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/macrostructures.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/structure.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/component-cookbook.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/layout-and-space.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/verbs/redesign.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/responsive.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/preview-examples.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/**\\\",\\\".opencode/co