uration, easing, spring, stagger, tooltip, toast, or drag recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/motion.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/microinteractions.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/interaction-and-states.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/motion.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/assets/interface-motion-{presentation.txt,auto.yaml}\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-motion/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/{register.md,design-token-vocabulary.md}\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/design-system-artifact-contract.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/ux-quality-reference.md\\\"],\\\"nextFocus\\\":\\\"Compare Hallmark's curated theme and design-DNA mechanics against the styles corpus, relational-exemplar authority, and design-reference schema without creating presets.\\\"}\\n\",\"additions\":1,\"deletions\":0}],\"diagnostics\":{},\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"Success. Updated the following files:\\nM .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl\",\"time\":{\"start\":1784528436222,\"end\":1784528436226}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_078e14388ae0b27f016a5dbe2747208191a808e565a568394b\"}},\"id\":\"prt_f7e2ec996001CtVQW2qtXsR51Y\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_081d9a116ffeOaaf4nAKEvxUgB\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e2e9c41001mVuSWizKGCHzf4\"}}\n{\"type\":\"step_finish\",\"timestamp\":1784528437353,\"sessionID\":\"ses_081d9a116ffeOaaf4nAKEvxUgB\",\"part\":{\"id\":\"prt_f7e2f0067001JBvOxvRbhgfDy4\",\"reason\":\"tool-calls\",\"snapshot\":\"fe03b20dde9c4dbba7dc0e6f79ecce2c3c838fcc\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e2e9c41001mV