{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784528952045,"sessionID":"ses_08202bafbffe7aMYl1BZMs5SAo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_qfHjJVzFWqS6tH33nnRj8IYA","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 7\n+\n+Read lineage state, strategy, registry, and relevant prior iterations first. Execute one LEAF iteration.\n+\n+## Focus\n+Compare Hallmark's twenty-theme catalog, four genre guides, optional per-theme specs, theme-selection logic, custom-theme fallback, and theme-aware behavior against sk-design's extracted styles corpus (reported around 1,290 bundles), styles DB/engine retrieval and rights gates, relational-exemplar authority, register contract, design-interface corpus adapter, and foundations token model. Determine whether a curated-theme model is a useful complement to the extracted corpus. Be precise about corpus cardinality from actual files/metadata, selection semantics, explainability, rights/provenance, anti-preset boundaries, and how curated archetypes could serve as labels or evaluation lenses without becoming copyable presets. Produce candidate rows and a concrete coexistence recommendation with exact target files, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\n+\n+## Writes\n+Only `iterations/iteration-007.md`, one append-safe iteration-7 state record, and `deltas/iter-007.jsonl` under the detached lineage. No other writes or sub-agents. Use separate file creation plus byte-preserving state append. Max 12 calls.\n+\n+Include corpus/theme comparison matrix, Candidate Matrix, Ruled Out, Dead Ends, exact citations, and next focus. Route proof exactly: `target_agent:\"deep-research\"`, `resolved_route:\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\"`. Delta first line equals state. Verify unique run 7.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,14 @@\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 7\n+\n+Read lineage state, strategy, registry, and relevant prior iterations first. Execute one LEAF iteration.\n+\n+## Focus\n+Compare Hallmark's twenty-theme catalog, four genre guides, optional per-theme specs, theme-selection logic, custom-theme fallback, and theme-aware behavior against sk-design's extracted styles corpus (reported around 1,290 bundles), styles DB/engine retrieval and rights gates, relational-exemplar authority, register contract, design-interface corpus adapter, and foundations token model. Determine whether a curated-theme model is a useful complement to the extracted corpus. Be precise about corpus cardinality from actual files/metadata, selection semantics, explainability, rights/provenance, anti-preset boundaries, and how curated archetypes could serve as labels or evaluation lenses without becoming copyable presets. Produce candidate rows and a concrete coexistence recommendation with exact target files, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\n+\n+## Writes\n+Only `iterations/iteration-007.md`, one append-safe iteration-7 state record, and `deltas/iter-007.jsonl` under the detached lineage. No other writes or sub-agents. Use separate file creation plus byte-preserving state append. Max 12 calls.\n+\n+Include corpus/theme comparison matrix, Candidate Matrix, Ruled Out, Dead Ends, exact citations, and next focus. Route proof exactly: `target_agent:\"deep-research\"`, `resolved_route:\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\"`. Delta first line equals state. Verify unique run 7.\n\n","files":[{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md","relativePath":".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md","type":"add","patch":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,14 @@\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 7\n+\n+Read lineage state, strategy, registry, and relevant prior iterations first. Execute one LEAF iteration.\n+\n+## Focus\n+Compare Hallmark's twenty-theme catalog, four genre guides, optional per-theme specs, theme-selection logic, custom-theme fallback, and theme-aware behavior against sk-design's extracted styles corpus (reported around 1,290 bundles), styles DB/engine retrieval and rights gates, relational-exemplar authority, register contract, design-interface corpus adapter, and foundations token model. Determine whether a curated-theme model is a useful complement to the extracted corpus. Be precise about corpus cardinality from actual files/metadata, selection semantics, explainability, rights/provenance, anti-preset boundaries, and how curated archetypes could serve as labels or evaluation lenses without becoming copyable presets. Produce candidate rows and a concrete coexistence recommendation with exact target files, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\n+\n+## Writes\n+Only `iterations/iteration-007.md`, one append-safe iteration-7 state record, and `deltas/iter-007.jsonl` under the detached lineage. No other writes or sub-agents. Use separate file creation plus byte-preserving state append. Max 12 calls.\n+\n+Include corpus/theme comparison matrix, Candidate Matrix, Ruled Out, Dead Ends, exact citations, and next focus. Route proof exactly: `target_agent:\"deep-research\"`, `resolved_route:\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\"`. Delta first line equals state. Verify unique run 7.\n","additions":14,"deletions":0}],"diagnostics":{},"truncated":false},"title":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-007.md","time":{"start":1784528952041,"end":1784528952044}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_056cc601e4af0189016a5dc03062e88191812854a9e5c2f765"}}