k or automatic theme rotation in sk-design\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"memory_match_triggers (connection closed)\\\",\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/custom-theme.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/genres/*.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/themes/{cobalt,hum}.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/LICENSE\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/README.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_retrieval-manifest.json\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_engine/{style-library,eligibility,cards}.mjs\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_db/README.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/{register.md,corpus-context/corpus-context-plan.mjs}\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/{SKILL.md,corpus/README.md,corpus/relational-exemplar.mjs,references/aesthetics/README.md}\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/{SKILL.md,corpus/README.md,references/design-system-artifact-contract.md}\\\"],\\\"nextFocus\\\":\\\"Compare Hallmark roadmap proposals for brand-first workflows, data visualization, tactile interaction, image hooks, and expanded variants against shipped sk-design ownership.\\\",\\\"createdAt\\\":\\\"2026-07-20T00:00:00Z\\\"}\\n*** End Patch\"},\"error\":\"apply_patch verification failed: Error: Failed to find expected lines in /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl:\\n{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":6,\\\"run\\\":6,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"execution\\\":\\\"single_i