{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784529861596,"sessionID":"ses_08202bafbffe7aMYl1BZMs5SAo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_b2OGXFI1kTCkMYPeNAP8Fxnq","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-008.md\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 8\n+\n+Read state and prior findings first. Execute one LEAF iteration only.\n+\n+## Focus\n+Evaluate Hallmark ROADMAP proposals for `hallmark variant`, brand-first flow -> generated design.md, theme-aware motion tokens, structural cookbook, codebase study, multi-page coherence, explainability/negative capability, and emotion-first prompting against actual shipped sk-design modes and `/interface:*` commands. Determine which are already shipped, which deserve surgical strengthening in existing commands/references, which are genuinely new, and which should be skipped. Reconcile with prior conclusions: no separate redesign/variant command, curated themes cannot become presets, measured extraction remains canonical, and semantic motion modifiers belong in existing assets. Produce roadmap rows with exact target paths and phased dependencies.\n+\n+## Writes\n+Only `iterations/iteration-008.md`, one append-safe run-8 state record, and `deltas/iter-008.jsonl` inside the detached lineage. Use direct write-once files and byte-preserving append; do not use combined/context-dependent patches. No other writes or sub-agents. Max 12 calls.\n+\n+Include Roadmap Matrix, Candidate Matrix, Ruled Out, Dead Ends, exact citations, value/effort/licensing, and next focus. Canonical route proof exact with target `deep-research`; delta first equals state; verify unique run 8.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated th