tion, async-state, interruption, reduced-motion, and performance rules are absent or weaker in shipped sk-design?\\\",\\\"Does any gap justify a new command or preset catalog?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Adopt a native semantic motion-modifier schema in existing Motion and Foundations assets, but reject Hallmark's named theme multipliers as presets.\\\",\\\"Shipped Motion is stronger on route-level interruption/reversal, async state modeling, reduced-motion semantic parity, and performance verification; card propagation and three async feedback checks are the narrow gaps.\\\",\\\"No new command is justified; all useful changes fit existing Motion, Foundations, and Interface owners.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"A new theme-motion, microinteraction, interaction-state, or reduced-motion command\\\",\\\"Hallmark's ten-theme duration multiplier table as presets\\\",\\\"A universal eight-state mandate for every interactive element\\\",\\\"Hallmark's global 150ms-important reduced-motion recipe and absolute transform-opacity-only rule\\\",\\\"Copying exact duration, easing, spring, stagger, tooltip, toast, or drag recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/motion.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/microinteractions.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/interaction-and-states.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/motion.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/assets/interface-motion-{presentation.txt,auto.yaml}\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-motion/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/{register.md,design-token-vocabulary.md}\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/design-system-artifact-contract.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/ux-quality-reference.md\\\"],\\\"nextFocus\\\":\\\"Compare Hallmark's curated theme and design-DNA mechanics against the styles corpus, relational-exemplar authority, and design-reference schema without creating presets.\\\"}\\n {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":6,\\\"run\\\":6,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"execution\\\":\\\"single_iteration\\\",\\\"state_source\\\":\\\"externalized_files\\\",\\\"do_not_switch_mode\\\":true,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark study, design-DNA schema, portable design.md, export formats, and styles ingestion versus shipped MD-GENERATOR\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":10,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.84,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Seven findings establish new field-level gaps, extension boundaries, or ingestion/export decisions and three refine known pipeline superiority into exact schema/report changes; the computed 0.85 is reduced to 0.84 because output-case authority was partially established in iteration 1.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which Hallmark design-DNA fields already exist, are absent, are weaker than measured extraction, or should be skipped?\\\",\\\"How should screenshot and URL diagnosis complement rather than replace the canonical extract-write-validate pipeline?\\\",\\\"Which provenance, motion, texture, risk, export, naming, and styles-ingestion changes are justified?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Hallmark diagnosis vocabulary is useful metadata, but shipped Playwright/computed-CSS extraction and tokens.json remain the value authority.\\\",\\\"Structural summary, visible provenance, measured Motion projection, optional texture/risk observations, and separate DTCG/shadcn exporters are bounded candidates.\\\",\\\"Uppercase DESIGN.md and curated six-artifact styles ingestion remain canonical; lowercase aliases, estimated screenshot tokens, preset catalogs, and automatic ingestion are rejected.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Replacing measured browser extraction with screenshot vision or shallow WebFetch diagnosis\\\",\\\"Writing image-estimated values into canonical tokens.json\\\",\\\"Importing Hallmark macrostructure, archetype, theme, reveal, treatment, or anti-pattern catalogs as v3 enums\\\",\\\"Lowercase design.md as an interchangeable canonical artifact\\\",\\\"Reusing tokens.json for DTCG or embedding all exports in DESIGN.md\\\",\\\"Inventing shadcn status tokens\\\",\\\"Automatic styles corpus ingestion\\\",\\\"Treating attestation as copyright proof or measurement confidence\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/study.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/design-md.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/export-formats.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/docs/study-examples.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/README.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/LICENSE\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design-reference.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/design-md-format.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/extraction-workflow.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/schema-v3.ts\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/types.ts\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/README.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_db/README.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_db/indexer.mjs\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_engine/manifest.mjs\\\"],\\\"nextFocus\\\":\\\"Compare Hallmark curated themes and genre selection against styles corpus retrieval/facets 