 assets now have exact target files, a COPY/ADAPT/LEARN/INSPIRE-NEW/SKIP verdict, a surgical change, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\\\",\\\"The highest-value gaps are signature-role hero selection, validated custom-craft evidence, fallback font metrics, authored-direction depth, and target-derived responsive proof.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\",\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\",\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\",\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\",\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"memory_match_triggers (timeout)\\\",\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"bash\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/color.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/typography.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/copy.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/imagery-kit.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/custom-theme.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/custom-craft.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/hero-enrichment.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/floating-nav.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/responsive.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/color/palette-theming.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/assets/token-starter.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/type/typography-system.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/layout/layout-responsive.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/layout/adaptation-matrix.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/des