tate modeling, reduced-motion semantic parity, and performance verification; card propagation and three async feedback checks are the narrow gaps.\\\",\\\"No new command is justified; all useful changes fit existing Motion, Foundations, and Interface owners.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"A new theme-motion, microinteraction, interaction-state, or reduced-motion command\\\",\\\"Hallmark's ten-theme duration multiplier table as presets\\\",\\\"A universal eight-state mandate for every interactive element\\\",\\\"Hallmark's global 150ms-important reduced-motion recipe and absolute transform-opacity-only rule\\\",\\\"Copying exact duration, easing, spring, stagger, tooltip, toast, or drag recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/motion.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/microinteractions.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/interaction-and-states.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/motion.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/assets/interface-motion-{presentation.txt,auto.yaml}\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-motion/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/{register.md,design-token-vocabulary.md}\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/design-system-artifact-contract.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/ux-quality-reference.md\\\"],\\\"nextFocus\\\":\\\"Compare Hallmark's curated theme and design-DNA mechanics against the styles corpus, relational-exemplar authority, and design-reference schema without creating presets.\\\"}\\n {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":6,\\\"run\\\":6,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\