":87,\"cache\":{\"write\":0,\"read\":158208}},\"cost\":0}}\nOK iteration 8 complete: narrative + route-proof + delta\n[deep-research] detected 5 legacy-import question(s) in key-questions; append external questions to research/inbox.jsonl instead.\n{\"iterationsCompleted\":8}\n","metadata":{"output":"...\n\ng extraction, anti-preset, or motion boundaries?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Variant and explain are shipped jobs; brand-first authored systems and project-path render adaptation are genuinely new boundaries; multi-page coherence, semantic motion, structural fingerprints, negative-capability rationale, and emotion intake fit existing owners.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Separate redesign, variant, study, or explain commands\\\",\\\"A public variant alias when directions already owns the job\\\",\\\"Generated brand values inside measured Style Reference DESIGN.md\\\",\\\"Hallmark themes, motion multipliers, emotion labels, or structural sketches as presets\\\",\\\"A new multi-page extraction relationship type\\\"],\\\"focusTrack\\\":\\\"roadmap-and-capability-boundary\\\",\\\"edgeCase\\\":\\\"artifact-authority\\\",\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"Glob\\\",\\\"Read\\\",\\\"Grep\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/ROADMAP.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design-reference.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/motion.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/procedures/{aesthetic-direction,variation-set}.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/{brief-to-dials,variation-diversity,real-ui-loop}.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/authoring-boundary.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/{types,design-boundary-detect}.ts\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/{assets/token-sta