ry or responsive overlap into exact existing-file changes; (6 + 3*0.5) / 9 = 0.83.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which of the nine named Hallmark assets adds a real capability beyond shipped Interface and Foundations guidance?\\\",\\\"What exact existing file should own each useful rule without adding commands or presets?\\\",\\\"Which reuse choices require Hallmark notice or separate third-party rights handling?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"All nine named Hallmark assets now have exact target files, a COPY/ADAPT/LEARN/INSPIRE-NEW/SKIP verdict, a surgical change, value, effort, and licensing treatment.\\\",\\\"The highest-value gaps are signature-role hero selection, validated custom-craft evidence, fallback font metrics, authored-direction depth, and target-derived responsive proof.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Copying Hallmark fixed palettes, font catalogs, theme catalog, craft recipes, hero archetype catalog, or floating-nav timing values\\\",\\\"Treating fixed 320/375/414/768 widths as universal breakpoints\\\",\\\"Hotlinking or redistributing the Hallmark imagery kit\\\",\\\"Copying attributed third-party voice samples\\\",\\\"Adding a standalone redesign, variant, theme, craft, hero, or floating-nav command\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"memory_match_triggers (timeout)\\\",\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"bash\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/color.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/typography.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/copy.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/imagery-kit.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/custom-theme.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/custom-craft.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/hero-enrichment.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/floating-nav.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/responsive.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/color/palette-theming.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/assets/token-starter.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/type/typography-system.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/layout/layout-responsive.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/layout/adaptation-matrix.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/procedures/aesthetic-direction.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/procedures/prototype-flow-spec.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/creation-contract.md\\\"],\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-07-20T06:10:06.551Z\\\",\\\"durationMs\\\":780000}\\n {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":5,\\\"run\\\":5,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"execution\\\":\\\"single_iteration\\\",\\\"state_source\\\":\\\"externalized_files\\\",\\\"do_not_switch_mode\\\":true,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark motion, microinteractions, and interaction states versus shipped Motion, /interface:motion, Foundations tokens, and Interface state guidance\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":8,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.81,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Five findings establish new file-level gaps or ownership decisions and three refine known motion overlap into exact surgical targets; (5 + 3*0.5) / 8 = 0.81 after rounding.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Are Hallmark's theme-aware motion tokens worth adopting, and where should they live?\\\",\\\"Which motion, microinteraction, async-state, interruption, reduced-motion, and performance rules are absent or weaker in shipped sk-design?\\\",\\\"Does any gap justify a new command or preset catalog?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Adopt a native semantic motion-modifier schema in existing Motion and Foundations assets, but reject Hallmark's named theme multipliers as presets.\\\",\\\"Shipped Motion is stronger on route-level interruption/reversal, async state modeling, reduced-motion semantic parity, and performance verification; card propagation and three async feedback checks are the narrow gaps.\\\",\\\"No new command is justified; all useful changes fit existing Motion, Foundations, and Interface owners.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"A new theme-motion, microinteraction, interaction-state, or reduced-motion command\\\",\\\"Hallmark's ten-theme duration multiplier table as presets\\\",\\\"A universal eight-state mandate for every interactive element\\\",\\\"Hallmark's global 150ms-important reduced-motion recipe and absolute transform-opacity-only rule\\\",\\\"Copying exact duration, easing, spring, stagger, tooltip, toast, or drag recipes\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/motion.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/microinteractions.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/interaction-and-states.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/motion.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/assets/interface-motion-{presentation.txt,auto.yaml}\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-motion/**\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/{register.md,design-token-vocabulary.md}\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/design-system-artifact-contract.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/assets/interface-preflight-card.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/ux-quality-reference.md\\\"],\\\"nextFocus\\\":\\\"Compare Hallmark's curated theme and design-DNA mechanics against the styles corpus, relational-exemplar authority, and design-reference schema without creating presets.\\\"}\\n {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":6,\\\"run\\\":6,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"execution\\\":\\\"single_iteration\\\",\\\"state_source\\\":\\\"externalized_files\\\",\\\"do_not_switch_mode\\\":true,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark study, design-DNA schema, portable design.md, export formats, and styles ingestion versus shipped MD-GENERATOR\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":10,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.84,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Seven findings establish new field-level gaps, extension boundaries, or ingestion/export decisions and three refine known pipeline superiority into exact schema/report changes; the computed 0.85 is reduced to 0.84 because output-case authority was partially established in iteration 1.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which Hallmark design-DNA fields already exist, are absent, are weaker than measured extraction, or should be skipped?\\\",\\\"How should screenshot and URL diagnosis complement rather than replace the canonical extract-write-validate pipeline?\\\",\\\"Which provenance, motion, texture, risk, export, naming, and styles-ingestion changes are justified?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Hallmark diagnosis vocabulary is useful metadata, but shipped Playwright/computed-CSS extraction and tokens.json remain the value authority.\\\",\\\"Structural summary, visible provenance, measured Motion projection, optional texture/risk observations, and separate DTCG/shadcn exporters are bounded candidates.\\\",\\\"Uppercase DESIGN.md and curated six-artifact styles ingestion remain canonical; lowercase aliases, estimated screenshot tokens, preset catalogs, and automatic ingestion are rejected.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Replacing measured browser extraction with screenshot vision or shallow WebFetch diagnosis\\\",\\\"Writing image-estimated values into canonical tokens.json\\\",\\\"Importing Hallmark macrostructure, archetype, theme, reveal, treatment, or anti-pattern catalogs as v3 enums\\\",\\\"Lowercase design.md as an interchangeable canonical artifact\\\",\\\"Reusing tokens.json for DTCG or embedding all exports in DESIGN.md\\\",\\\"Inventing shadcn status tokens\\\",\\\"Automatic styles corpus ingestion\\\",\\\"Treating attestation as copyright proof or measurement confidence\\\"],\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"read\\\",\\\"glob\\\",\\\"grep\\\",\\\"bash\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/study.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/design-md.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/export-formats.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/docs/study-examples.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/README.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/LICENSE\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design-reference.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/design-md-format.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/references/extraction-workflow.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/schema-v3.ts\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/types.ts\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/README.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_db/README.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_db/indexer.mjs\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_engine/manifest.mjs\\\"],\\\"nextFocus\\\":\\\"Compare Hallmark curated themes and genre selection against styles corpus retrieval/facets and relational-exemplar authority without creating presets.\\\",\\\"durationMs\\\":0,\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-07-20T06:27:05Z\\\",\\\"sessionId\\\":\\\"fanout-sol-opencode-1784525177424-b0sf31\\\",\\\"generation\\\":1}\\n {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":7,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"execution\\\":\\\"single_iteration\\\",\\\"state_source\\\":\\\"externalized_files\\\",\\\"do_not_switch_mode\\\":true,\\\"run\\\":7,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark curated themes and genre/custom selection versus the 1,290-bundle sk-design corpus, retrieval rights gates, and relational-exemplar authority\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":7,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.86,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Five findings were fully new and two partially refined prior anti-preset conclusions; (5 + 2*0.5) / 7 = 0.86.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Is Hallmark's curated twenty-theme model a useful complement to sk-design's extracted styles corpus, and if so how should the two models coexist?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Curated archetypes are useful only as independently authored derived labels, explanations, and evaluation lenses after rights-gated retrieval; they must not become selectors, presets, value sources, or rights overrides.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Importing Hallmark theme names, genre labels, token combinations, or detailed theme specifications as sk-design facets or presets\\\",\\\"A user-visible curated-theme chooser or silent archetype fallback on corpus no-fit\\\",\\\"Allowing labels to bypass provenance or exact-reuse rights, average source values, or generate target tokens\\\",\\\"Treating all twenty Hallmark themes as equally specified\\\"],\\\"focusTrack\\\":\\\"architecture\\\",\\\"edgeCase\\\":\\\"contradictory-evidence\\\",\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"Read\\\",\\\"Grep\\\",\\\"Glob\\\",\\\"Bash\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/SKILL.md:230-354\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/custom-theme.md:1-79\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/themes/*.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/genres/*.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/styles/_db/README.md:1-65\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md:170-206\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/corpus/README.md:1-30\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/aesthetics/README.md:24-28\\\",\\\"Python pathlib corpus census command\\\"],\\\"timestamp\\\":\\\"2026-07-20T06:42:52.416086Z\\\",\\\"durationMs\\\":600000,\\\"graphEvents\\\":[]}\\n+{\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":8,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"execution\\\":\\\"single_iteration\\\",\\\"state_source\\\":\\\"externalized_files\\\",\\\"do_not_switch_mode\\\":true,\\\"run\\\":8,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark ROADMAP proposals versus shipped sk-design modes and /interface:* commands\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":9,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.72,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Four findings establish genuinely new capability or contract boundaries and five materially refine already-shipped overlap into exact targets; (4 + 5*0.5) / 9 = 0.72 after rounding.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which named Hallmark ROADMAP proposals are already shipped, deserve surgical strengthening, are genuinely new, or should be skipped?\\\",\\\"What exact paths and phased dependencies should own surviving proposals without violating extraction, anti-preset, or motion boundaries?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Variant and explain are shipped jobs; brand-fi