or skips?\\\",\\\"What licensing, security, provenance, and phase gates constrain surviving candidates?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"assets.md warrants a provider-neutral asset provenance and hosting receipt, not a copied source catalog.\\\",\\\"contract.md contributes a narrow stylesheet-entrypoint preservation handoff; preview-examples.md should be skipped as a preset-bearing catalog.\\\",\\\"Data visualization and live preview are already shipped under stronger owners; generated media is an existing Interface branch plus external transport; tactile and sound need narrow owner-level checks; haptics should be deferred until a named runtime and user-value path exist.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Provider catalogs or volatile price/license tables in sk-design\\\",\\\"Nanobanana-specific core hook or prompt-hash cache\\\",\\\"Reusable Plate or tactile themes\\\",\\\"A second data-viz file or charts command\\\",\\\"A new live-preview MCP server\\\",\\\"General web haptics guidance without a supported target runtime\\\",\\\"Treating generated-media watermark or reference input as rights proof\\\"],\\\"focusTrack\\\":\\\"remaining-assets-and-future-integrations\\\",\\\"edgeCase\\\":\\\"transport-capability-versus-product-value\\\",\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"Glob\\\",\\\"Read\\\",\\\"Grep\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/assets.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/contract.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/skills/hallmark/references/preview-examples.md\\\",\\\"external/hallmark/ROADMAP.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-foundations/references/data-viz.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/real-ui-loop.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/references/design-process/copy-and-mock-data.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/shared/sk-code-handoff.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-mcp-open-design/referenc