{"type":"text","timestamp":1784530608463,"sessionID":"ses_08202bafbffe7aMYl1BZMs5SAo","part":{"id":"prt_f7e501e390013ER5MGYqf69rV2","messageID":"msg_f7e50071f001E620tLZTo1B9dF","sessionID":"ses_08202bafbffe7aMYl1BZMs5SAo","type":"text","text":"Nine iterations now cover licensing, all five mode mappings, slop gates, design-DNA extraction, the exact 1,290-bundle corpus, and roadmap integrations. Iteration 10 is the forced-depth reconciliation pass: it will audit per-asset matrix coverage, resolve contradictions, rank adoptions, and define phase/acceptance dependencies before workflow synthesis.","time":{"start":1784530607673,"end":1784530608461},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"msg_0647f101fe09a18d016a5dc6af9e6c8191aba85319271335d8","phase":"commentary"}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1784530618023,"sessionID":"ses_08202bafbffe7aMYl1BZMs5SAo","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"apply_patch","callID":"call_BbqzV2AQ5IeJmbkXJma474p2","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"patchText":"*** Begin Patch\n*** Add File: .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-010.md\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 10\n+\n+Read config/state/strategy/registry and all nine prior iteration narratives/deltas first. Execute exactly one final LEAF research iteration; do not write final `research.md` because synthesis remains workflow-owned.\n+\n+## Focus\n+Perform a coverage and contradiction audit across the complete Hallmark inventory and prior findings. Ensure every Hallmark root reference, verb, schema, gate set, theme/genre model, macrostructure/component family, and ROADMAP idea has at least one final matrix disposition: Hallmark asset | exact sk-design target mode/command/reference | COPY / ADAPT / LEARN / INSPIRE-NEW / SKIP | concrete change | value | effort | licensing treatment. Consolidate duplicates without losing per-asset rows. Resolve contradictory candidate details from separate iterations (for example theme labels, motion token placement, brand-first authored artifacts, image/provider integrations, route-proof wording is not research content). Rank the highest-value adoptions with reasons, dependencies, and measurable acceptance gates. Produce a phased plan that favors surgical existing-mode changes before optional new capabilities. Explicitly list residual unknowns and items requiring legal/rights or product-demand confirmation.\n+\n+## Writes\n+Only `iterations/iteration-010.md`, one append-safe run-10 state record, and `deltas/iter-010.jsonl` inside the lineage. Direct write-once creation and byte-preserving append only; no combined/context patch. No sub-agents or other writes. Max 12 calls.\n+\n+Required narrative sections: Coverage Audit, Reconciled Reuse Matrix, Contradictions Resolved, Ranked Adoptions, Phased Plan Inputs, Acceptance Gates, Residual Unknowns, Ruled Out, Dead Ends, Sources Consulted, Assessment. Use exact canonical route proof (`deep-research`, no `@`, exact standard resolved-route string). Delta first line equals state and includes structured findings/ruled_out rows. Verify unique run 10 and all ten iteration artifacts before returning.\n*** End Patch"},"output":"Success. Updated the following files:\nA .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-010.md","metadata":{"diff":"Index: /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-010.md\n===================================================================\n--- /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-010.md\n+++ /Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/prompts/iteration-010.md\n@@ -0,0 +1,14 @@\n+DEEP-RESEARCH\n+Resolved route: mode=research; target_agent=@deep-research; execution=single_iteration; state_source=externalized_files; do_not_switch_mode=true\n+\n+# Deep-Research Iteration 10\n+\n+Read config/state/strategy/registry and all nine prior iteration narratives/deltas first. Execute exactly one final LEAF research iteration; do not write final `research.md` because synthesis remains workflow-owned.\n+\n+## Focus\n+Perform a coverage and contradiction audit across the complete Hallmark invento