5TiSDhene9oBC\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"read\",\"callID\":\"call_jo5RDwx7NvAleuBaxsX1KrYj\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"filePath\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl\",\"offset\":9,\"limit\":4},\"output\":\"<path>/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl</path>\\n<type>file</type>\\n<content>\\n9: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":8,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"execution\\\":\\\"single_iteration\\\",\\\"state_source\\\":\\\"externalized_files\\\",\\\"do_not_switch_mode\\\":true,\\\"run\\\":8,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Hallmark ROADMAP proposals versus shipped sk-design modes and /interface:* commands\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":9,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.72,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Four findings establish genuinely new capability or contract boundaries and five materially refine already-shipped overlap into exact targets; (4 + 5*0.5) / 9 = 0.72 after rounding.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which named Hallmark ROADMAP proposals are already shipped, deserve surgical strengthening, are genuinely new, or should be skipped?\\\",\\\"What exact paths and phased dependencies should own surviving proposals without violating extraction, anti-preset, or motion boundaries?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Variant and explain are shipped jobs; brand-first authored systems and project-path render adaptation are genuinely new boundaries; multi-page coherence, semantic motion, structural fingerprints, negative-capability rationale, and emotion intake fit existing owners.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Separate redesign, variant, study, or explain commands\\\",\\\"A public variant alias when directions already owns the job\\\",\\\"Generated brand values inside measured Style Reference DESIGN.md\\\",\\\"Hallmark themes, motion multipliers, emotion labels, or structural sketches as presets\\\",\\\"A new multi-page extraction relationship type\\\"],\\\"focusTrack\\\":\\\"roadmap-and-capability-boundary\\\",\\\"edgeCase\\\":\\\"artifact-authority\\\",\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"Glob\\\",\\\"Read\\\",\\\"Grep\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/ROADMAP.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design-reference.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/motion.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/procedures/{ae... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n10: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":9,\\\"run\\\":9,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"execution\\\":\\\"single_iteration\\\",\\\"state_source\\\":\\\"externalized_files\\\",\\\"do_not_switch_mode\\\":true,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Remaining Hallmark assets and roadmap boundaries for data visualization, tactile craft, generated media, preview transport, sound, and haptics\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":8,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.67,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Three findings establish new operational boundaries and six materially refine known owner/transport overlap; (3 + 6*0.5) / 9 = 0.67 after rounding.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which unmapped Hallmark root assets add durable value beyond shipped sk-design owners?\\\",\\\"Which remaining roadmap proposals are existing-mode adap