ntract boundaries and five materially refine already-shipped overlap into exact targets; (4 + 5*0.5) / 9 = 0.72 after rounding.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which named Hallmark ROADMAP proposals are already shipped, deserve surgical strengthening, are genuinely new, or should be skipped?\\\",\\\"What exact paths and phased dependencies should own surviving proposals without violating extraction, anti-preset, or motion boundaries?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"Variant and explain are shipped jobs; brand-first authored systems and project-path render adaptation are genuinely new boundaries; multi-page coherence, semantic motion, structural fingerprints, negative-capability rationale, and emotion intake fit existing owners.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Separate redesign, variant, study, or explain commands\\\",\\\"A public variant alias when directions already owns the job\\\",\\\"Generated brand values inside measured Style Reference DESIGN.md\\\",\\\"Hallmark themes, motion multipliers, emotion labels, or structural sketches as presets\\\",\\\"A new multi-page extraction relationship type\\\"],\\\"focusTrack\\\":\\\"roadmap-and-capability-boundary\\\",\\\"edgeCase\\\":\\\"artifact-authority\\\",\\\"toolsUsed\\\":[\\\"skill\\\",\\\"Glob\\\",\\\"Read\\\",\\\"Grep\\\",\\\"apply_patch\\\"],\\\"sourcesQueried\\\":[\\\"external/hallmark/ROADMAP.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/design-reference.md\\\",\\\".opencode/commands/interface/motion.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/SKILL.md\\\",\\\".opencode/skills/sk-design/design-interface/procedures/{ae... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n10: {\\\"type\\\":\\\"iteration\\\",\\\"iteration\\\":9,\\\"run\\\":9,\\\"mode\\\":\\\"research\\\",\\\"target_agent\\\":\\\"deep-research\\\",\\\"agent_definition_loaded\\\":true,\\\"resolved_route\\\":\\\"Resolved route: mode=research target_agent=deep-research\\\",\\\"execution\\\":\\\"single_iteration\\\",\\\"state_source\\\":\\\"externalized_files\\\",\\\"do_not_switch_mode\\\":true,\\\"status\\\":\\\"complete\\\",\\\"focus\\\":\\\"Remaining Hallmark assets and roadmap boundaries for data visualization, tactile craft, generated media, preview transport, sound, and haptics\\\",\\\"findingsCount\\\":8,\\\"newInfoRatio\\\":0.67,\\\"noveltyJustification\\\":\\\"Three findings establish new operational boundaries and six materially refine known owner/transport overlap; (3 + 6*0.5) / 9 = 0.67 after rounding.\\\",\\\"keyQuestions\\\":[\\\"Which unmapped Hallmark root assets add durable value beyond shipped sk-design owners?\\\",\\\"Which remaining roadmap proposals are existing-mode adaptations, genuine capabilities, external integrations, deferrals, or skips?\\\",\\\"What licensing, security, provenance, and phase gates constrain surviving candidates?\\\"],\\\"answeredQuestions\\\":[\\\"assets.md warrants a provider-neutral asset provenance and hosting receipt, not a copied source catalog.\\\",\\\"contract.md contributes a narrow stylesheet-entrypoint preservation handoff; preview-examples.md should be skipped as a preset-bearing catalog.\\\",\\\"Data visualization and live preview are already shipped under stronger owners; generated media is an existing Interface branch plus external transport; tactile and sound need narrow owner-level checks; haptics should be deferred until a named runtime and user-value path exist.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Provider catalogs or volatile price/license tables in sk-design\\\",\\\"Nanobanana-specific core hook or prompt-hash cache\\\",\\\"Reusable Plate or tactile themes\\\",\\\"A second data-viz file or charts command\\\",\\\"A new live-preview MCP server\\\",\\\"General web haptics guidance without a supported target runtime\\\",\\\"Treating generated-media watermark or reference input as rights proof\\\"],\\\"focusTrack\\\":\\\"remaining-assets-and-future-integrations\\\",\\\"edgeCa... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\\n11: {\\\"type\\\":\\