nded optional capabilities, deferrals, and skips.\\\"],\\\"ruledOut\\\":[\\\"Direct COPY as the default strategy\\\",\\\"New duplicate modes, commands, or preview server\\\",\\\"Hallmark catalogs as presets, selectors, facets, bundles, enums, or fallback values\\\",\\\"Authored or screenshot-estimated values in measured artifacts\\\",\\\"Provider locks, volatile catalogs, hotlinking, or rights-by-attestation\\\"],\\\"focusTrack\\\":\\\"coverage-contradiction-and-plan-inputs\\\",\\\"edgeCase\\\":\\\"contradictor... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\",\"lineStart\":9,\"lineEnd\":11,\"totalLines\":11,\"truncated\":false}},\"title\":\".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl\",\"time\":{\"start\":1784531225878,\"end\":1784531225881}},\"metadata\":{\"openai\":{\"itemId\":\"fc_0670e4bb1b47b49a016a5dc91961cc8191b2723ac47457e498\"}},\"id\":\"prt_f7e598ce5001lInvu3muEpc4Mu\",\"sessionID\":\"ses_081af800effe15TiSDhene9oBC\",\"messageID\":\"msg_f7e5904ac001VBUdGzuveOPrBG\"}}\n{\"type\":\"tool_use\",\"timestamp\":1784531225966,\"sessionID\":\"ses_081af800effe15TiSDhene9oBC\",\"part\":{\"type\":\"tool\",\"tool\":\"bash\",\"callID\":\"call_zr6pR704eNn3lkHwDTrn4D9p\",\"state\":{\"status\":\"completed\",\"input\":{\"command\":\"git status --short -- \\\".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode\\\" && git diff --name-only -- \\\".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode\\\"\",\"workdir\":\"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public\"},\"output\":\"?? .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/\\n\",\"metadata\":{\"output\":\"?? .opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/\\n\",\"exit\":0,\"truncated\":false},\"title\":\"git statu