-markdown\"\n149:     },\n150:     {\n151:       \"text\": \"How should curated themes and the extracted styles corpus coexist, if at all?\",\n152:       \"addedAtIteration\": 1,\n153:       \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n154:     },\n155:     {\n156:       \"text\": \"Which roadmap items are true gaps rather than duplicates of shipped procedures or infrastructure?\",\n157:       \"addedAtIteration\": 1,\n158:       \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n159:     },\n160:     {\n161:       \"text\": \"Which registry candidates survive fixture design without overlapping existing tells or creating broad false positives?\",\n162:       \"addedAtIteration\": 2,\n163:       \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n164:     },\n165:     {\n166:       \"text\": \"Which Hallmark interface/foundations structural systems improve generation-time direction without duplicating audit-time checks?\",\n167:       \"addedAtIteration\": 2,\n168:       \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n169:     },\n170:     {\n171:       \"text\": \"Where should a future Hallmark MIT notice live if implementation chooses substantial textual reuse despite the idea-level recommendation?\",\n172:       \"addedAtIteration\": 2,\n173:       \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n174:     }\n175:   ],\n176:   \"uncoveredQuestions\": [\n177:     \"What does Hallmark's license permit us to copy, adapt, and redistribute, and what attribution or notice obligations apply?\",\n178:     \"Which Hallmark assets map to sk-design interface, foundations, audit, md-generator/design-reference, and motion, and what concrete gaps exist in each target?\",\n179:     \"Which Hallmark slop gates, pre-emit critique heuristics, schemas, motion tokens, and design-DNA fields are absent or weaker in sk-design?\",\n180:     \"Is Hallmark's curated twenty-theme model a useful complement to sk-design's extracted styles corpus, and if so how should the two models coexist?\",\n181:     \"Which redesign, variant, brand-first, data-visualization, tactile, and image-hook roadmap ideas merit existing-mode adaptation, new capabilities, or rejection?\"\n182:   ],\n183:   \"keyFindings\": [],\n184:   \"ruledOutDirections\": [\n185:     {\n186:       \"id\": \"ruled-out-834ff2c37453\",\n187:       \"text\": \"**Ruled out:** Treating Hallmark's portable `design.md` as evidence that shipped `sk-design` lacks a design-reference pipeline. The shipped md-generator already has a measured extract-write-validate backend and explicit v3 schema. [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md:230-259] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/schema-v3.ts:90-120]\",\n188:       \"contentHash\": \"834ff2c37453\",\n189:       \"addedAtIteration\": 1\n190:     },\n\n(Showing lines 1-190 of 706. Use offset=191 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"sessionId\": \"fanout-sol-opencode-1784525177424-b0sf31\",\n  \"parentSessionId\": null,\n  \"lineageMode\": \"new\",\n  \"generation\": 1,\n  \"continuedFromRun\": null,\n  \"terminalStop\": {\n    \"stopReason\": \"maxIterationsReached\",\n    \"totalIterations\": 10,\n    \"answeredCount\": 5,\n    \"totalQuestions\": 5,\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-07-20T07:12:37.761Z\"\n  },\n  \"keyQuestions\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-1-what-does-hallmark-s-license-permit-us-to-copy-adapt-and-redistribute-and-what-a\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"What does Hallmark's license permit us to copy, adapt, and redistribute, and what attribution or notice obligations apply?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",","truncated":true,"loaded":[],"display":{"type":"file","path":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/findings-registry.json","text":"{\n  \"sessionId\": \"fanout-sol-opencode-1784525177424-b0sf31\",\n  \"parentSessionId\": null,\n  \"lineageMode\": \"new\",\n  \"generation\": 1,\n  \"continuedFromRun\": null,\n  \"terminalStop\": {\n    \"stopReason\": \"maxIterationsReached\",\n    \"totalIterations\": 10,\n    \"answeredCount\": 5,\n    \"totalQuestions\": 5,\n    \"timestamp\": \"2026-07-20T07:12:37.761Z\"\n  },\n  \"keyQuestions\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-1-what-does-hallmark-s-license-permit-us-to-copy-adapt-and-redistribute-and-what-a\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"What does Hallmark's license permit us to copy, adapt, and redistribute, and what attribution or notice obligations apply?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",\n      \"injectedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"promotedQuestionId\": null,\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"resolvedAtIteration\": null,\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-2-which-hallmark-assets-map-to-sk-design-interface-foundations-audit-md-generator-\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"Which Hallmark assets map to sk-design interface, foundations, audit, md-generator/design-reference, and motion, and what concrete gaps exist in each target?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",\n      \"injectedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"promotedQuestionId\": null,\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"resolvedAtIteration\": null,\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-3-which-hallmark-slop-gates-pre-emit-critique-heuristics-schemas-motion-tokens-and\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"Which Hallmark slop gates, pre-emit critique heuristics, schemas, motion tokens, and design-DNA fields are absent or weaker in sk-design?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",\n      \"injectedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"promotedQuestionId\": null,\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"resolvedAtIteration\": null,\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-4-is-hallmark-s-curated-twenty-theme-model-a-useful-complement-to-sk-design-s-extr\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"Is Hallmark's curated twenty-theme model a useful complement to sk-design's extracted styles corpus, and if so how should the two models coexist?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",\n      \"injectedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"promotedQuestionId\": null,\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"resolvedAtIteration\": null,\n      \"resolved\": false\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-5-which-redesign-variant-brand-first-data-visualization-tactile-and-image-hook-roa\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"Which redesign, variant, brand-first, data-visualization, tactile, and image-hook roadmap ideas merit existing-mode adaptation, new capabilities, or rejection?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",\n      \"injectedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"promotedQuestionId\": null,\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"resolvedAtIteration\": null,\n      \"resolved\": false\n    }\n  ],\n  \"openQuestions\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-1-what-does-hallmark-s-license-permit-us-to-copy-adapt-and-redistribute-and-what-a\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"What does Hallmark's license permit us to copy, adapt, and redistribute, and what attribution or notice obligations apply?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",\n      \"injectedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"promotedQuestionId\": null,\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"resolvedAtIteration\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-2-which-hallmark-assets-map-to-sk-design-interface-foundations-audit-md-generator-\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"Which Hallmark assets map to sk-design interface, foundations, audit, md-generator/design-reference, and motion, and what concrete gaps exist in each target?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",\n      \"injectedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"promotedQuestionId\": null,\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"resolvedAtIteration\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-3-which-hallmark-slop-gates-pre-emit-critique-heuristics-schemas-motion-tokens-and\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"Which Hallmark slop gates, pre-emit critique heuristics, schemas, motion tokens, and design-DNA fields are absent or weaker in sk-design?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",\n      \"injectedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"promotedQuestionId\": null,\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"resolvedAtIteration\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-4-is-hallmark-s-curated-twenty-theme-model-a-useful-complement-to-sk-design-s-extr\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"Is Hallmark's curated twenty-theme model a useful complement to sk-design's extracted styles corpus, and if so how should the two models coexist?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",\n      \"injectedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"promotedQuestionId\": null,\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"resolvedAtIteration\": null\n    },\n    {\n      \"id\": \"question-5-which-redesign-variant-brand-first-data-visualization-tactile-and-image-hook-roa\",\n      \"inboxId\": null,\n      \"text\": \"Which redesign, variant, brand-first, data-visualization, tactile, and image-hook roadmap ideas merit existing-mode adaptation, new capabilities, or rejection?\",\n      \"origin\": \"legacy-import\",\n      \"source\": \"key-questions\",\n      \"injectedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"promotedQuestionId\": null,\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 0,\n      \"resolvedAtIteration\": null\n    }\n  ],\n  \"resolvedQuestions\": [],\n  \"carriedForwardOpenQuestions\": [\n    {\n      \"text\": \"Which Hallmark assets are genuinely stronger or absent after file-level comparison with each mode?\",\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 1,\n      \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\": \"Where substantial reuse is recommended, what exact target path and MIT notice mechanism should accompany it?\",\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 1,\n      \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\": \"Which slop gates, critique heuristics, schema fields, motion tokens, and design-DNA fields merit COPY, ADAPT, LEARN, INSPIRE-NEW, or SKIP?\",\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 1,\n      \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\": \"How should curated themes and the extracted styles corpus coexist, if at all?\",\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 1,\n      \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\": \"Which roadmap items are true gaps rather than duplicates of shipped procedures or infrastructure?\",\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 1,\n      \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\": \"Which registry candidates survive fixture design without overlapping existing tells or creating broad false positives?\",\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 2,\n      \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\": \"Which Hallmark interface/foundations structural systems improve generation-time direction without duplicating audit-time checks?\",\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 2,\n      \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"text\": \"Where should a future Hallmark MIT notice live if implementation chooses substantial textual reuse despite the idea-level recommendation?\",\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 2,\n      \"source\": \"iteration-markdown\"\n    }\n  ],\n  \"uncoveredQuestions\": [\n    \"What does Hallmark's license permit us to copy, adapt, and redistribute, and what attribution or notice obligations apply?\",\n    \"Which Hallmark assets map to sk-design interface, foundations, audit, md-generator/design-reference, and motion, and what concrete gaps exist in each target?\",\n    \"Which Hallmark slop gates, pre-emit critique heuristics, schemas, motion tokens, and design-DNA fields are absent or weaker in sk-design?\",\n    \"Is Hallmark's curated twenty-theme model a useful complement to sk-design's extracted styles corpus, and if so how should the two models coexist?\",\n    \"Which redesign, variant, brand-first, data-visualization, tactile, and image-hook roadmap ideas merit existing-mode adaptation, new capabilities, or rejection?\"\n  ],\n  \"keyFindings\": [],\n  \"ruledOutDirections\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"ruled-out-834ff2c37453\",\n      \"text\": \"**Ruled out:** Treating Hallmark's portable `design.md` as evidence that shipped `sk-design` lacks a design-reference pipeline. The shipped md-generator already has a measured extract-write-validate backend and explicit v3 schema. [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/SKILL.md:230-259] [SOURCE: .opencode/skills/sk-design/design-md-generator/backend/scripts/schema-v3.ts:90-120]\",\n      \"contentHash\": \"834ff2c37453\",\n      \"addedAtIteration\": 1\n    },","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":190,"totalLines":706,"truncated":true}},"title":".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/findings-registry.json","time":{"start":1784531577585,"end":1784531577596}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_07d380d10adf7375016a5dca7970f481918439bffa1fac4ae2"}},"id":"prt_f7e5eea96001RTHfbaCVEY4HnF","sessionID":"ses_08202bafbffe7aMYl1BZMs5SAo","messageID":"msg_f7e5ea7710016UBlZWKzoflvvK"}}
