{"type":"text","timestamp":1784531629336,"sessionID":"ses_08202bafbffe7aMYl1BZMs5SAo","part":{"id":"prt_f7e5f704100173HR1Ao2reZ3BQ","messageID":"msg_f7e5f343a001wvDsad3kcnXsnc","sessionID":"ses_08202bafbffe7aMYl1BZMs5SAo","type":"text","text":"## Objective\n- Complete the detached 10-iteration Hallmark-to-sk-design deep-research lineage and synthesis.\n- Write only under `.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode`, then output `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:sol-opencode`.\n\n## Important Details\n- Session: `fanout-sol-opencode-1784525177424-b0sf31`.\n- Executor: `cli-opencode`, model `openai/gpt-5.6-sol-fast`.\n- Stop policy: `max-iterations`; threshold `0.05` was telemetry only.\n- Hallmark is MIT-licensed; copies/substantial portions require its copyright and permission notice.\n- No paths outside the lineage may be modified.\n- Final response must be exactly one line.\n- Canonical executor import failed with `ERR_MODULE_NOT_FOUND: .../jsonl-repair.js`; direct detached `opencode run` fallback was used successfully.\n- Reducer was safely redirected to the lineage by monkeypatching `resolveArtifactRoot` in-process.\n\n## Work State\n### Completed\n- Loaded `deep-research` and `cli-opencode`; confirmed OpenCode `1.18.3`, OpenAI auth, and model availability.\n- Initialized config, JSONL state, strategy, registry, iteration/delta/prompt directories.\n- Completed and mechanically verified all 10 iteration narratives, route-proof records, and delta files.\n- Ran reducer after each successful iteration.\n- Produced a 61-row reconciled asset matrix and ranked/phased recommendations.\n- Created `research.md` with licensing verdict, matrix, ranked adoptions, phased plan, acceptance gates, eliminated alternatives, divergence map, open questions, and convergence report.\n- Emitted `resource-map.md`.\n- Set `deep-research-config.json` status to `complete`.\n- Appended `synthesis_complete` with `stopReason:\"maxIterationsReached\"`.\n- Latest reducer result: `status:\"COMPLETE\"`, `iterations:10`.\n\n### Active\n- Final packet reconciliation and validation.\n- Reducer currently reports `resolvedQuestions:0`, `openQuestions:5`, `keyFindings:0` despite completed synthesis.\n- Strategy questions were marked `[x]`, but reducer retained legacy unresolved registry entries.\n- `resource-map.md` reports 10 missing paths because several citations were normalized as packet-relative filenames.\n\n### Blocked\n- Synthesis invariant would fail while `findings-registry.json` has zero `keyFindings` despite nonzero iteration findings.\n- No external blocker; packet-local reconciliation is required.\n\n## Next Move\n1. Reconcile `findings-registry.json` and `deep-research-dashboard.md` so 5 questions are resolved, 0 remain open, and key findings reflect the ranked synthesis; avoid rerunning the reducer afterward unless the source records are normalized first.\n2. Validate config/state JSON, exactly 10 unique iterations, all narratives/deltas, `research.md`, `resource-map.md`, terminal event, write boundary, and then output only `FANOUT_LINEAGE_COMPLETE:sol-opencode`.\n\n## Relevant Files\n- `.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/research.md`: canonical synthesis and deliverable.\n- `.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-config.json`: immutable run contract, now status `complete`.\n- `.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-state.jsonl`: 10 iteration records plus terminal synthesis event.\n- `.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deep-research-strategy.md`: checked questions and completion focus.\n- `.opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/findings