led_out\",\"iteration\":10,\"id\":\"no-catalog-authority\",\"direction\":\"Import Hallmark themes, genres, macrostructures, or components as presets or value authority\",\"reason\":\"This conflicts with subject grounding, rights gates, and no-preset boundaries.\",\"sources\":[\"iteration-007.md:64-74\"]}","lineStart":1,"lineEnd":10,"totalLines":11,"truncated":true}},"title":".opencode/specs/sk-design/014-hallmark-design-skill-research/001-research/research/lineages/sol-opencode/deltas/iter-010.jsonl","time":{"start":1784531738814,"end":1784531738821}},"metadata":{"openai":{"itemId":"fc_0a80ffbfaeb793e7016a5dcb1a5e788191a964d13ff5e167a4"}},"id":"prt_f7e6160a0001w22NJWT21c6IwH","sessionID":"ses_08202bafbffe7aMYl1BZMs5SAo","messageID":"msg_f7e61101c001p39nC9gETldYI2"}}
